<HEADLINE> Nigeria's Olympic Contigent Awarded </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LAGOS, August 9 (Xinhua) -- Nigeria's Head of State General
Sani Abacha today showered awards on the athletes, officials and
members of the Supporters' Club who represented the country in
the centennial olympics just concluded in Atlanta, the United
States.
