<TEXT>
<P>
YICHANG, August 10 (Xinhua) -- A newly-built suspension bridge
across the Three Gorges at the middle reaches of the Yangtze River
opened to traffic today.
</P>
<P>
The Xiling Yangtze River Bridge at the downstream of the dam of
the Three Gorges Project has a single span of 900 meters, and is
1,118.66 meters long and 18.5 meters wide.
</P>
<P>
