<HEADLINE> Fujian's Exports Expected To Reach 10 Billion US Dollars </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
FUZHOU, August 10 (Xinhua) -- The value of Fujian Province's
exports is expected to hit 10 billion US dollars this year, a
local trade official announced here today.
</P>
<P>
Foreign-funded enterprises have become a vital new force in the
province with a combined export value reaching 2.3 billion US
dollars in the first half of the year, 14.8 percent over the same
period of last year.
</P>
